a Project</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">,</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt"> are available at: </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">http://www.athenaforum.org.uk/reports.htm</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 28.35pt; text-indent:-28.35pt"><a name="_ftn11"></a><a href="#_ftnref11">[11]</a><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10pt">              </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt; font-weight:normal">Good Practice in University Chemistry Departments, Royal Society of Chemistry, London, 2004 (</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt; font-weight:normal">http://www.rsc.org/images/chemdeptsreport_tcm18-16919.pdf</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt; font-weight:normal">); Planning for Success - Good Practice in University Science Departments, Royal Society of Chemistry, London, 2008 (</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt; font-weight:normal">http://www.rsc.org/images/GoodPractice_tcm18-127915.pdf</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt; font-weight:normal">)</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 28.35pt; text-indent:-28.35pt"><a name="_ftn12"></a><a href="#_ftnref12">[12]</a><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt; font-style:normal">Advancing women in mathematics: good practice in UK university departments</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt; font-style:normal">, London Mathematical Society, London, 2013 (</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt; font-style:normal">http://www.nationalstemcentre.org.uk/res/documents/page/Stem-graduates-in-non-stem-jobs.pdf</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt; font-style:normal">)</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size